	<div class="commentBody">
		<div id="comment_body_64277890"><p>If the various planets are communicating with each other, and using something resembling a beam of photons to do it, most of the scatter that escapes is going to be in or near the plane of their planetary system. If they're not using beams, it matters less, but they probably are. We do.</p></div>
